oai_dc:dc.dc:title: ARTIFICIAL BEACH NOURISHMENT ON THE GERMAN NORTH SEA COAST
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Kramer, Johann
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: artificial nourishment
German Coast
beach nourishment
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Several artificial beach nourishments were completed during the last twenty years on the German North Sea coast. Investigations made it possible to settle different problems connected with artificial beach nourishment and to gain additional information and experience. At present beach nourishments at Langeoog and Sylt will be realized in a way which is expected to bring the highest effectiveness. The hydrodynamic processes in connection with these beach nourishments and their change in shape will be subject to the paper.
